data.description: Discover a perfect family home in Silver Palm, featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and attractive amenities. With spacious bedrooms and well-appointed bathrooms, this two-story corner lot property provides a cozy and practical living space. The kitchen boasts a stunning island, and the backyard holds tremendous potential for your vision. Silver Palm is a sought-after community with top schools, parks, and a tranquil ambiance. Seize the opportunity to own this charming property and shape it to your liking. Contact us for a viewing and embrace the Silver Palm lifestyle.
